{"id":3552,"date":"2025-03-04T12:26:36","date_gmt":"2025-03-04T12:26:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/?p=3552"},"modified":"2025-04-02T14:53:01","modified_gmt":"2025-04-02T14:53:01","slug":"covid-response-for-staff-and-patients","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/2025\/03\/04\/covid-response-for-staff-and-patients\/","title":{"rendered":"NHST Covid Response for Staff and Patients"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"3552\" class=\"elementor elementor-3552\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f09f71f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"f09f71f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8571225 elementor-hidden-desktop dce_masking-none elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8571225\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/DoR_Marking_Heaty-1024x1024.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3553\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/DoR_Marking_Heaty-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/DoR_Marking_Heaty-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/DoR_Marking_Heaty-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/DoR_Marking_Heaty-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/DoR_Marking_Heaty.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db04d90 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"db04d90\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-ogsc=\"rgb(0, 36, 81)\"><p>Staff at Ninewells Hospital benefited from more than \u00a3130,000 of funding to help them during the recovery from the coronavirus pandemic.<\/p><p>\u00a367,000 went to spiritual care and wellbeing services. It helped increase capacity for activities, as staff looked for support in dealing with the Covid-19 crisis.<\/p><p>\u2018Extra pressure\u2019 on wellbeing service during Covid. Alan Gibbon, previous head of the staff wellbeing service, said: \u201cOur wellbeing services is the primary route for staff to seek one-to-one support within NHS Tayside. \u201cThe staff wellbeing service\u2026 has been under increased pressure to provide a timely response to staff support<\/p><p>\u201cThis has been a growing situation due to the ongoing Covid pandemic and the extra pressure this is placing on the service.\u201d<\/p><p>\u00a363,000 was awarded to the building of a new outdoor pavilion, where staff were able to meet, have lunch and enjoy workshops.<\/p><p>Mary Colvin, chair of the board of trustees for Ninewells Community Garden, said:<\/p><p>\u201cEveryone involved in running the garden is delighted to receive this award, which will allow us to further develop our work to support the health and care staff as they deliver the Covid recovery plan. \u201cGrabbing some time in the working day to have a walk and get outside is just the tonic to relieve stress.\u201d<\/p><p>It comes after staff at several sites across Tayside were provided with new outdoor benches thanks to money from NHS Tayside Charitable Foundation.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Staff at Ninewells Hospital benefited from more than \u00a3130,000 of funding to help them during the recovery from the coronavirus pandemic.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":3553,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[12,6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3552","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-case-study","category-projects"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3552","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3552"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3552\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3624,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3552\/revisions\/3624"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3553"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3552"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3552"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nhstayside.foundation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3552"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}